java_data_structures API

This project contains common computer science data structures and some of their associated algorithms:

  • Stack
  • Queue
  • List
  • Set
  • Map
  • Graph
  • Tree
Packages 
Package Description
structures.commons
Contains all of the shared interfaces throughout the library.
structures.graphs
Provides implementations of all combinations of weighted, unweighted, directed and undirected graphs.
structures.maps
Implementations of maps using different types of hashing techniques such as chaining, double hashing, linear probing, and quadratic probing.
structures.sets
A package that contains different implementations of the set data structure.
structures.trees
A library of different tree implementations, mostly binary trees.
structures.vectors
The core linear (vector-like) data structures in computer science.
